      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG BOY JETT (4) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 35.33 beating BLUE MOON MARIE. Awkwardly drawn but likes the trip. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Will go close again if runs up to latest. BLUE MOON MARIE (3) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.3 lengths back in second (35.42) at this track in a Other over 600m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. COMPTON ROCKY (7) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (35.67) at this track. Can measure up this time. WEBLEC SHIRALEE (1) placed last time out at big odds - worth considering.",
